HEADWORD: Peridiastole
<hw>Per`i*di*as"to*le</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<fld>(Physiol.)</fld> <def>The almost inappreciable time which elapses
between the systole and the diastole of the heart.</def>⟦br⟧
